storyInfo: Ambushed by a large group of bandits on a mission, Captain Akafuyu is hurt, and the enemy is waiting to pounce. After a moment of hesitation, with her teammates' encouragement, Kirara takes a stand...

attributes.content: How are they?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: That leader girl got slashed from behind by the bandits. Still out for the moment.
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: That many, all sneaking up on one woman at once. Cowards!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: S—So what now?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: What do you mean what now? Those thieves were after our medicine, so they want us dead!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: I'll take them on if it comes to that, my life against theirs! I can use Arts myself...
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: They live by getting one over! We couldn't even light a flame if we wanted. Taking them on would never get anywhere...
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Even if it wouldn't, we've got to! You saying you want those bloodthirsty cutthroats to make off with our medicine, after we barely managed to buy it?
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: All our efforts just to buy this one cheap measly lot of suppressants! And I want you to imagine, if it wasn't for them, then you, me, the village at large, how long we'll still be alive for all these damn stones in us!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Not to mention, there's Rhodes Islanders with us...
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: But Rhodes is only here to deliver the drugs!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: You get it straight. Once they put the drugs in our hands, they could go at any time. They wouldn't help us!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: And even if they did stay... You've seen how badly the leader got hurt, after how easily she dealt with the beasts. Now it's just those girls left—what do you think they're going to be able to do?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: The bandits aren't going to just forgive and forget after failing to steal our drugs. They might attack again at any moment!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Better we give them whatever they want. Better than dooming us all. We—We can always figure out something else!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Think carefully about this Rhodes Island or whatever. With how cheap they're selling it, who knows if the drugs are real or fake...
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Enough! You can shut up any day!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Erk.
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: I didn't hear this lousy tune from you when those girls helped us fend off the beasts AFTER dropping off the medicine, or when that doctor girl gave you an examination!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: You think the measly amount we forked over was worth them delivering it all the way out here, and bringing a doctor to do checkups free of charge?
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: If that's the lengths Rhodes Island will go to, then whether or not the medicine works, I'm still believing in them!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Tell me, then... You think we can actually protect these drugs?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: We can only try.
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Now, enough. I'm going to help the Rhodes Islanders. You find something to busy yourself with.
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Fine. One of the girls asked me to help out this morning. Still a little work left to go. I'll fetch somebody else to come with.
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: (Not good. This is totally not good, the way things are going.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Captain's KO'd and hurt, treatment takes time, now all we've got is a DPS and also me, a weird support character without many use cases...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Wait, no, nononobad. This is a really serious situation, I can't talk about it like a game.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (But... I mean, this is hard. This is a tough one...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: *sigh*
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: What's the sigh for?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Wgaagh!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Phew, uh, okay, it's you, Utage...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: In the flesh.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: (Please don't pop up behind me without warning like that, you're going to jumpscare me to death.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (What are you, a ninja or something?)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Did I spook you? Soz.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Come on, though, I'm not some kinda ninja.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Wha? Huh?
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (How did she know what I was thinking...?)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (It couldn't be... mindreading?!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I don't have superpowers or anything, you're just, like, real easy to read, girl.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: (You're kidding me. Can you really tell?)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Yeah, for real real.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: (Well, that's convenient, now I don't need to talk.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Hey, slow down, Kirara.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: It's not a conversation unless you say what you're thinking out loud.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Or, like, what, do you want me to just stare at you forever? Hmm?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Okay, joke's over.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: I'm gonna go check up on Akafuyu. See ya in a bit~
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Uh...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Hold on, Utage!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: I'm coming with you.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: So, uh, Utage... what do you think about the situation we're in right now?
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Um... pretty messed up, I guess.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: We were expecting a normal delivery mission, right? So, not like we prepared that much.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: We did get a team put together...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Buuut the captain was our big hitter, and she left a whole opening to get backstabbed in.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Haaa...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I have no laughs in me right now.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Usually, average bandits aren't, like, a match for us at all, but they've got way too many guys. Kind of out of my league, if I had to solo them.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Our doctor's not gonna do combat, and you...
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Don't look at me, I'm a Logistics techie.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Oh, word? I always feel like every tech I know's pretty good in a fight.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Besides, you were good at those strategy games, weren't you? And you and the Doctor broke some kinda record one time? So, like, maybe being a commander's your thing.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: What do you think? Wanna try?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Me?
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: You're joking, real life isn't a video game, I... I can't.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: We should probably go see how Akafuyu's doing.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Aww... it's a bad habit to casually shoot yourself down.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Besides, you've totally got ideas going, don't you?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: So hard to be honest, Kirara.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: The wound won't pose much issue, and we've applied anti-inflammatory.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: She still hasn't come around, but as long as she's not got a fever, then she should be out of the woods after convalescing properly.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Oh, okay...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: That's great to hear.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: But, like, how much longer is our captain gonna sleep for?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: That's up to Akafuyu's own constitution. We've given her all the treatment we can, but the wound was very deep...
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Even if she does wake up, she can't return to combat straight away.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Hmm? We can't just wave her in anyway?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: No!
attributes.name: Honeyberry & Kirara

attributes.content: *sigh*...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: The sensors I laid out indicate those bandits have been in the area the whole time. We did get in touch with a nearby squad, but it's still gonna be a while before they get here.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: If the bandits attack now, while the time is ripe, I think we might...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Might be done for.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: So now what? You think we take the captain and retreat?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Wait, if we go, what about the Infected here?
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: We've delivered the medication, so that's mission complete, but I can't just leave the villagers for dead.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Hmm... we take the medication too?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Okay, putting aside whether or not they'd buy that as a ruse, I think the bandits are after more than the meds anyway. They can fight the people here, and they have literally no way to fight back.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: That's true...
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: So, uh...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Actually, I think we could—
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Excuse me, I've brought you all some food...
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: A little place like ours doesn't have much, so if you can just put up with it.
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Thank you, it's kind to worry about us. Was anyone from the village hurt in the previous attack?
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: We're all fine, thanks to your group.
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Can I ask how your captain's doing?
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: No worries, she's not in danger now.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Oh, okay, that's a massive relief!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Right, can't forget this too.
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: It's those topographic maps of the place you all wanted...
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Huh? Topographic maps? I didn't hear anything about that.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: I didn't request any either... Did Akafuyu ask for them at some point?
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: ...It was me.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Thanks.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: The voice of gratitude is near-inaudible.
Silent since the villager entered the room, the girl seems in a rush to dodge all lines of sight, dropping her gaze to the maps she now holds.
Being hand-drawn by the Infected of the wild settlement, they are rough and crude, no more than a few abstract lines drawn as hints in parts; they could hardly amount to real topographies.
Absorbing correct information from maps like these would be far from easy.
But grasping them tight, the Higashinese girl comes off like a truly experienced hand, rapidly flipping through the sheets.
Mmhuh...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Majorly flat terrain, very disadvantageous to us.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (But there's places here to exploit for sure... like here. If we can do a little setup here...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (The plan works, it's feasible. But...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: So? Did you work something out?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Attagirl, Kirara~ Look at you, you got something brewing in your head, don't you?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: What?! Really? Girl, you... no! Miss, you have an idea?!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: ...I think we...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Uh...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: What did she even wanna say? She was just stammering. Say something or get off.
attributes.name: Listless Guy

attributes.content: Just wasting time... You can't even hear how quiet she talks!
attributes.name: Listless Guy

attributes.content: I know, right? I heard in seventh grade, she was absent, uh, so much she almost repeated. She never showed up to class. Everyone thought she did something to make the school suspend her, like literally, everyone.
attributes.name: Caustic Girl

attributes.content: *snort* Apparently she likes those little plastic figures too. What if she was just secretly doing something, like, gross at home? Wow... creepy.
attributes.name: Caustic Girl

attributes.content: And her name totally doesn't fit, right? Like, you know you see it and you think Kirara, like she's gonna be this sparkly kinda pretty girl? But actually, she's just Kirara the weird downcast depresso. Such a buzzkill.
attributes.name: Gossipy Student

attributes.content: Her face? She never even lifts her head, who knows what her face is like...?
attributes.name: Gossipy Student

attributes.content: Kirara, the school has resolved that we can't tolerate you being absent from class again like last year.
attributes.name: Anxious Teacher

attributes.content: If you can't adapt to school life, we may have to consider getting in touch with your parents about you repeating a year, or even withdrawing from school entirely...
attributes.name: Anxious Teacher

attributes.text: Stop looking at me like that.

attributes.content: No...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I, I d... I don't know...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (I can't breathe...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (What am I doing? Just say your words, come on, you're not at school here...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Uh, ah... I'd like to suggest—
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: B—Bad news!!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: The bandits! The bandits are back! They're surrounding the entrance, they've hurt some of us too...
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: What?!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: There's wounded? Where? I need you to take me there immediately!
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Guess that's that. I'm coming too.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Hey, Kirara.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Don't keep us waiting too long.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: (Freaking Utage talking, it's like she understands everything.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (What's the deal? I haven't figured this out myself yet...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (No, I can't just stand here like an idiot, I've got to do something or other and it's simple as that!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Urgh...
Eek!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Don't make such a fuss.
Ssss... owowow, I can feel my wound.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Akafuyu?! You're up?!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: How's your wound, are you okay? D-D-D-Don't move! Quick, lie down!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Just lie back down, I'll call for Honeyberry right away—
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Come back, you needn't call anyone!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: I can hold on... I actually awoke quite a time ago, and I heard everything you talked about. No great issues press me—my body simply wouldn't heed me somewhat.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: If the bandits that assaulted me have delivered themselves to me, then good! Watch me cut them down!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Ourgh!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Tsss...
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: No, okay, great issues are extremely pressing you!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Quit moving! Aaaahh okay okay your wound's bleeding again... Stay still, put the katana down!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: You're in no condition to fight right now, at all, whatsoever! You think you're some kinda fighting game protag? As long as your health bar's not empty yet you're completely unaffected, is that it, huh??
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Tch... There, you can talk quite fine, can't you.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: What do we do, then? If I cannot go, I fear Utage will buckle before long.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Are you saying you have some plan?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: I—I've come up with it, kind of, but...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I don't think I can do it...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Fool. What is it you're so afraid of?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: What? I'm not...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: You are.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Out with your ideas! I will judge as the captain whether or not they work!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: On what basis do you say you can't do it? These squad members were handpicked by me. Are you saying I could not discern properly?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Wait, wait, I didn't I wasn't... You're twisting my words against me!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Yes, indeed. What is it? If you have objections, speak and let me hear.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: (Nnnnrgghh—)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (What the hell is her deal—!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I see you as quite the strategizer. I've never bested you once in that regard!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: But those were games...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Split no hairs. I recall you also discussed tactical command with that Doctor at one point?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: But that was on the topic of games too!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: And they've taught you plenty applicable in practice, no?!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Enough tarrying! Eyes wide! It's simple as this: will you do it?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: I've told you that I am the one who will judge here! I am your general in this moment, and you are my counsel. Now hasten in offering your advice!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Huff... hah...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: What... even... stammering...
attributes.name: Listless Guy

attributes.content: ......hear how quiet...
attributes.name: Listless Guy

attributes.content: ...absent......did something...
attributes.name: Caustic Girl

attributes.content: ...likes those......secretly...
attributes.name: Caustic Girl

attributes.content: ...totally doesn't fit......weird downcast... buzzkill...
attributes.name: Gossipy Student

attributes.content: ...who knows... like...
attributes.name: Gossipy Student

attributes.content: ...school has resolved...
attributes.name: Anxious Teacher

attributes.content: If...
attributes.name: Anxious Teacher

attributes.text: I don't care what people say, I don't give a care...
Yeah. Yeah, okay. Didn't I already decide?

attributes.content: (Deep breath)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I'll talk, I'll freaking talk okay?! Stop making this scene such a big emotional deal, does it seriously not embarrass you when everything starts hitting you like lines from a visual novel?!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I'll say it, I'm totally gonna say it!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I think we can—
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Someone else is hurt! Please get the wounded over to me, faster!
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Sorry, but I can't hold them off for too long either. We're gonna get surrounded like this.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Seriously, are our drugs worth this much?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Compared to other medications on the market, we sell really cheap... and the efficacy's guaranteed.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Oh, so that's why we send a whole squad on deliveries all the time.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Yes...
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: It's not just an issue of money. Medications like these are difficult to buy on the market period, so...
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: That's why there's Infected among the people robbing too.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Isn't there anything we can do...?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: O—Oh, right! That pink-haired girl had me set up a machine earlier! Is there something we can do with that?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Machine?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: I didn't hear anything about that.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Me neither.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: I think I'm getting deja vu.
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: But...!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Oh, if you wanna know about that...
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Why don't we just make her explain it herself?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Right, that's the Miss who asked us to do everything!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: (Phew... it's okay, I can do this, I can speak, it's okay...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: —Everyone, listen to me!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: I have a plan.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: *pant*... *pant*...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Found her! Over here!
attributes.name: Boorish Bandit

attributes.content: She's got all the drugs in her car! After her!
attributes.name: Boorish Bandit

attributes.content: (...hah, they followed.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (If the map was right, then around here there should be...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (No, wait!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (I have to go further north!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Phew...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Yep, okay, this is the area, this is some loose sand alright...!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (We make the sand subside here, and form quicksand...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Great!)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Thank you, Originium Arts. I think I could kinda fill a mage role like this, huh?)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Done! Next. I just stall for time a little...)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Need to find a place to hide myself.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Where'd she go?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Where's she hiding? The car's still here. Get all the drugs out!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Hey, girl, can you hear me?!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Ran out with the goods all alone, huh? Thought you could get away on a fluke, or are you just trying to lure us out?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: No matter your plan, it's nothing now!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: (What's the deal with this guy? He's a trash-talker.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: (Oh, if only I could tell him how every character who talks too much before a battle usually comes out of it pretty bad.)
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Hey! The med boxes here... they're all empty!
attributes.name: Boorish Bandit

attributes.content: We got tricked!
attributes.name: Boorish Bandit

attributes.content: Heh... expected that. Looks like she just wanted to string us along.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Shame for you, though. You can pretend you're on your solo adventure, but we're not as stupid as you think.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: You know how many of us chased your bait? Less than half.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: The rest of us probably broke through that lousy Infected village by now, I'm reckoning?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Uh... wow, you really can talk.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Honestly, I'm kind of starting to envy the sheer confidence you've gotta have in order to talk at your opponent like you're straight up giving a speech.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Oh? Who knew that's where you'd be hiding... What, not gonna run?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Don't care to, anymore.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Is it really going to work?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: This is all we've got. If, just if, it doesn't do anything...
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: What's to fear?! You heard Kirara's plan yourselves! The feasibility is tremendous!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: And lest we forget, I'm present too! A wounded general is hardly a rare sight... *hiss*
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Stop showing off, Akafuyu!
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Kirara already led a bunch of the guys away. The numbers on the rest...
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Mmhm, I think I should basically make it, even if we have issues.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: There you have it.
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: I estimate she saw this too, hence why her arrangements are so?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Okay, then, no time to lose.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Everyone ready? Push the switch... 'eyy!
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: What... What is that?!
attributes.name: Towering Bandit

attributes.content: That's a caster's Arts! Hey, are you suicidal? Pull out!
attributes.name: Vicious Bandit

attributes.content: Where did they find so many casters...?
attributes.name: Towering Bandit

attributes.content: Urgh!!
attributes.name: Towering Bandit

attributes.content: Watch out, girl. Arts aren't the only danger on the scene.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: What the hell kind of trick are you pulling?!
attributes.name: Vicious Bandit

attributes.content: We've been watching the whole time! There's no way you found a caster to help—
attributes.name: Vicious Bandit

attributes.content: Hm? Didn'tcha know? Infected can use Arts barehanded.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: You back these guys into a corner, and they can seriously do anything. You get me?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Oh, heyyy, lucky, everyone's actually Infected here.
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Guess how many'd rather burst into dust in your face than let you get your way, huh?
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Maniacs!
attributes.name: Vicious Bandit

attributes.content: These Infected are all insane! They're going to take us down with them!
attributes.name: Crumbling Bandit

attributes.content: Run for it!!
attributes.name: Crumbling Bandit

attributes.content: The bandits! They're beginning to retreat!
attributes.name: Irritable Infected

attributes.content: Really?! Oh, thank heavens...!
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Who knew this little box could be so much of a threat?
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Good skies, didn't that work a little too well?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: H—Honestly!
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: When we pressed it and the sound of Arts firing suddenly went off all around, even I was jumpy!
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: Using a preconstructed projector to intimidate the enemy! Trust her to think of it...
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: And arranged so perfectly in such a short span of time. How did she possibly do it?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Er, the pink-haired Miss asked us to install all these machines this morning.
attributes.name: Tense Infected

attributes.content: Pardon? This morning?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Wait, when we'd just become aware of the bandits, before anything had even happened?!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: What in the stances did the Doctor teach her...?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Aaaand it's time.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: What did you do?!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: This pit... pteuch, she's trapping us!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Help me! I'm going to get buried!
attributes.name: Boorish Bandit

attributes.content: Girl! Don't you care if they live or die?!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Even if you kill us all, the village is still—
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: You just keep going...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: What I want is a perfect clear.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: You wouldn't just ignore bait as obvious as me. Even if you didn't totally buy it, you'd at least send part of your people to follow, and that was enough.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: We trap a portion using me, a support who doesn't affect the big picture, which lowers your numbers, and back in the village we've got Utage for high attack, so they're pretty sure to handle it.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Not to mention the projectors...
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Wait, why am I explaining all this to you again?
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Explaining your own plan is what antags do, and then they mess it up and they get comeback'd on. NG, NG.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: What the hell kind of craziness are you talking to yourself about?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: You have a bind debuff, you don't get to interrupt!
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Hiii, Kirara, can you hear me~
attributes.name: Utage

attributes.content: Oi, Utage! No nonsense from you!
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Kirara, well done! We sorted things out handily on this side. How was yours?
attributes.name: Akafuyu

attributes.content: Kirara, you're not hurt, are you?
attributes.name: Honeyberry

attributes.content: ...Heheh.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: No, I'm fine, I'm untouched. All good on my end too.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: Ahem.
attributes.name: Kirara

attributes.content: ...Just as planned.
attributes.name: Kirara
